{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6cdf0fa9fc","title":"对《苏联专家对“多快好省”路线的看法》一文的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7d7ee1b5a4","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"9eece9f026","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央宣传部编印的《宣教动态》第63期刊载的《苏联专家对“多快好省”路线的看法》一文。文中说，4月25日下午宋任穷约集第二机械工业部在京的苏联专家座谈，向他们介绍了我国当前整风和大跃进情况，以及多快好省的建设路线、工农业并举、大中小结合的建设方针等，并列举了苏联专家协助我国贯彻多快好省路线的大量事例。苏联专家沃尔比约夫除在会上讲话外，会后向翻译说了一些意见。沃尔比约夫说：现在中国党提出的"},{"id":"6c786fcc2c","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记。"},{"id":"b20f3df5e1","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在《苏联专家对“多快好省”路线的看法》一文后写的说明。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8b4c1c7104","type":"title","text":"对《苏联专家对“多快好省路线的看法》一文“的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"9eece9f026","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"6c786fcc2c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请印发大会各同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"b20f3df5e1","type":"subtitle","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"cf13717aba","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日上午四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"36c9ec597a","type":"paragraph","text":"见今年第63期《宣教动态》。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"6f9b177d25","type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省”的建国方针是完全正确的。因为这主要是提高劳动生产率和加速","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"ae17456a26","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义建设的问题。他认为要做到“又多又省”这两点，必须结合当地情","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"41e5ca1c3a","type":"paragraph","text":"况。比如在苏联钢材很便宜，而木材很贵，但在中国却相反，木材很便宜，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"7fb369a8a1","type":"paragraph","text":"而钢材很贵。假如不了解这种实际情况，而提建设时都要用钢材，不用其他","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"64e6b5611b","type":"paragraph","text":"代用品，势必造成多花钱，就不合乎“多”“省”的精神。又如在苏联提倡搞","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"f1c0db78c5","type":"paragraph","text":"机械化、自动化的大型工厂，这是因为苏联人少，劳动力不够。但在中国就","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"cb46e04a53","type":"paragraph","text":"不一样，中国人多，现时如果也提倡像苏联一样搞机械化、自动化，就不合","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"9e663cc1a7","type":"paragraph","text":"乎中国国情。中国党现在提出多搞中型、小型厂矿企业的方针，是合乎中国","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"e9759ba5b5","type":"paragraph","text":"情况的。这样可以发挥每一个人的作用。在这以前，沃尔比约夫也说过，在·他与中国同志的接触中，常发现有些同志在工作中不动脑筋，主动考虑问题","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"8775a1a100","type":"paragraph","text":"不够，不管大事小事都要依靠专家来解决，甚至在讨论问题时；有些同志不","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"aa3f124871","type":"paragraph","text":"提出自己的见解和看法，而是只抄专家的答案，事后原封不动地去照办。这","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"89ba6fb51a","type":"paragraph","text":"不是创造性地学习先进经验，而是机械地搬用。因此，也就容易发生偏差，","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"e812285b52","type":"paragraph","text":"不合乎中国国情。专家只能起顾问和指导作用，许多问题还得中国同志自己","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"cba4b19384","type":"paragraph","text":"来解决，因为他们了解情况最清楚，同时也便于发挥本身的独立思考精神。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"},{"id":"192d6796d0","type":"paragraph","text":"这份材料作为会议文件在中共八大二次会议上印发。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc"}],"page":{"id":"79d21df105","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"6cdf0fa9fc","start":348,"end":349}}}},"__N_SSG":true}